snippet.title: Jayce The Bee Honey Jump App
snippet.description:
In a race against time, Jayce must retrieve the magical jewel from the clutches of the Wasp King. Collect the honey drops left behind by the Nectcia Jewel but “Bee” careful because there are obstacles at every turn. 
From the pages of the Jayce the Bee children’s books, Jayce once again shows that courage starts with “Bee-lieving” In this fun-filled game adaptation.
